 The mode must always be one of the following:
 <list type="bullet"><item><term><c><see cref="F:Android.Views.MeasureSpecMode.Unspecified" /></c></term></item><item><term><c><see cref="F:Android.Views.MeasureSpecMode.Exactly" /></c></term></item><item><term><c><see cref="F:Android.Views.MeasureSpecMode.AtMost" /></c></term></item></list></para>
          <para tool="javadoc-to-mdoc">
            <i>Note:</i> On API level 17 and lower, makeMeasureSpec's
 implementation was such that the order of arguments did not matter
